  ('optician-moex-00931', 'optician', 'optician-moex-110-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設一眼之屈光狀態為-2.50DS/-0.50DC×180，角膜曲度（keratometry）為43.50D@180/44.00D@090，若 選擇中心基弧（basecurveradius）43.00D硬式透氣隱形眼鏡（RGPlens），所需鏡片度數為何？', '["-2.00DS", "-2.25DS", "-2.50DS", "-3.00DS"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "79a1785aebea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c0d5dd75a323", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00932', 'optician', 'optician-moex-110-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '通常角膜塑形鏡片（orthokeratology,ortho-K）的直徑約10～11mm之間，此類鏡片屬於下列何者？', '["角膜鞏膜鏡（corneosclerallens）", "鞏膜鏡（sclerallens）", "微型鞏膜鏡（minisclerallens）", "角膜鏡（corneallens）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "79a1785aebea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c0d5dd75a323", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00933', 'optician', 'optician-moex-110-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '為驗配硬式高透氣隱形眼鏡，使用試戴片（基弧7.80 mm/鏡片光學區8.4mm/鏡片直徑9.4mm/度數 -3.00DS）雙眼皆達成理想配戴，而戴鏡驗光（over-refraction）1.0的度數為右眼-4.25DS/-0.50DC×180， 左眼-4.50DS/-0.75DC×180，插片頂點距離為12mm，則隱形眼鏡訂片的屈光度數最正確應為：', '["右眼-4.25DS，左眼-4.50DS", "右眼-4.50DS，左眼-4.75DS", "右眼-6.75DS，左眼-7.00DS", "右眼-7.25DS，左眼-7.50DS"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "79a1785aebea", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c0d5dd75a323", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110111", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第二梯次:110年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、社會工作師考試、110年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽...", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
